Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.71,0:00:16.52,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,No, I really did get a 32.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.52,0:00:18.37,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Then show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.76,0:00:21.46,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't we say we'd show our scores at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.46,0:00:23.62,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I showed you mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.62,0:00:26.63,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I got a 32...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.09,0:00:28.28,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.28,0:00:30.19,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,No, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:33.31,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,When you think about it, it's a 32.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:36.55,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I lie about such a {\i1}real{\i0} score?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:38.33,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,About a 32...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:40.22,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty-twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:41.68,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty-two, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:43.91,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:45.57,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave it at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.57,0:00:50.96,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I guess I can't do anything about whether you'll show me or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.96,0:00:53.63,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,My score was bad this time too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.63,0:00:55.59,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit shameless, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.59,0:00:57.07,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.57,0:01:07.95,Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,800)\pos(470,320)}An Everyday
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.60,0:01:07.95,Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,800)\pos(470,355)}Compliment
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:24.52,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:28.65,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Um... um... this is... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:39.74,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Yukko, as expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:45.71,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no, no... What I meant to say was, it's unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:49.17,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you forgot about your homework the day before yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:58.72,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, that's not right... You did your homework, but left it at home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:04.22,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:05.73,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,That's your attitude towards it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.46,0:02:09.60,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,You don't do your homework often, but you did this time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.21,0:02:13.11,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,You're just not very good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:15.48,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams and ambitions are like that too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:19.36,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,The first step is the hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:21.62,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you've done, Yukko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:24.83,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,You've cleared the first barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:27.20,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Ba... rrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:29.40,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, the barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.40,0:02:30.92,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,The first barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:34.85,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.85,0:02:36.51,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,...cleared it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:41.94,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, so you may not have realised that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:45.43,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Especially for an ordinary person, that's a very difficult thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:50.19,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:51.90,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,...guess I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:53.95,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,You did, you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:56.96,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,In all seriousness, that's something worthy of respect!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:03:01.99,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,But Mio-chan is even more amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:05.08,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,You always do your homework through force of habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:08.33,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a habit of mine to always do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:11.03,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I do it by force of habit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:14.96,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,By comparison, you {\i1}never{\i0} do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:20.27,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,This is{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.06,0:03:24.35,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,With this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:26.31,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I've got her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:29.18,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:30.68,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Yukko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:36.32,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Cars and even trains first need energy to start running.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:42.04,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,If you think of it like that, you might be hiding an incredible power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.86,0:03:46.20,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:48.29,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,...understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:51.93,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I mustn't rush it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:54.67,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Little by little... little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:03:57.12,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, Mio-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.12,0:03:59.42,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,You're overestimating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:02.32,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just an ordinary human.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:04.97,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I fail plenty of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:08.22,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I can get pretty depressed too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:10.76,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, you don't have to be so modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:12.56,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not modesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:16.44,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone already knows you're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:20.07,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,No, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:22.36,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what they call the will to challenge oneself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:25.70,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's not a total lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:27.37,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:34.21,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm absolutely no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:36.09,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,The manga I drew recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:39.59,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,...I started thinking that nobody would appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:42.95,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,So I got scared and couldn't submit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:46.05,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,You get nervous a lot, don't you Mio-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:50.72,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,You only got one point, so don't {\i1}you{\i0} say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:56.27,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Yukko, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:04:59.90,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:02.24,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Exam information.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:05.40,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,One: Give it your best effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:07.35,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's it! That's exactly it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:09.73,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,That's the most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:12.17,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,You always give it your best effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:14.87,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,You've grasped the most important aspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:16.37,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,But... I got one point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:21.50,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:25.72,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Yukko, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:30.49,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot the most important thing and got caught up in our scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:34.22,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Since you've already grasped that, I might have been jealous of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:36.02,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:38.66,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm already doing my homework through habit,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:41.87,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know whether or not I can give it my best in exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:42.94,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same for my manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:44.84,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,But you're different, Yukko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:47.03,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,You always give it your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:50.70,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,You're a breath of fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:06:01.08,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I'd really love to have your positive attitude, Yukko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:04.32,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, but that's all I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:06.97,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,But that's the most important thing, like I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:12.47,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you say so, I guess it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:18.73,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you work up the courage to take that first step?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:20.85,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:24.15,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I might say something bad though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:27.57,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you just have to avoid thinking negative thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:30.07,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,You need to have the will to always look ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.69,0:06:35.39,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Things that you can believe in are very important, and knowing that, you can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.87,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:38.61,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Always look ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:41.25,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as for me, I guess it came to me subconsciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:43.37,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, that's what's natural for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:47.28,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:48.13,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,A talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:51.68,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,That's your talent, Yukko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:54.87,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not a talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:58.06,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,But... maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.57,0:07:02.48,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I guess... that could be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:06.41,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,If it comes to you subconsciously, then it's something born into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:09.52,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,You can't gain it just through trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:11.86,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm envious of that talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:14.25,Sign1,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.7\fad(500,0)}Natural Talent
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:16.99,Sign1,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.7\fad(500,0)}Genius
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.42,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Mio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:23.33,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you {\i1}really{\i0} Mio-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:26.38,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you 100 yen. Or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:30.01,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:33.05,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could at least get a little of that blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:35.81,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:37.97,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't possibly give such a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.19,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:43.19,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably spreading the blessing around already, Yukko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:44.64,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:46.44,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:49.62,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,They say you should try everything out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:52.03,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:54.71,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I got a little of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:56.12,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,The courage to move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:59.14,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you're not going to achieve anything by praising me so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:00.91,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get some of my motivation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:03.79,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Yukko, your motivation is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:12.81,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:17.10,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be discouraged by only getting one point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:25.85,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I got away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.29,0:08:30.11,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, hers was only a lukewarm Heavenly Rock Cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.29,0:08:30.11,Default-Alt,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Note: In Japanese mythology, this is a reference to the cave where Amaterasu hid when angered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:33.28,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,If you set it up, she'll bite soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:36.22,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Well, all I did was randomly compliment her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:40.17,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope she studies a bit more after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:42.66,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Mio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:45.67,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I turned the source of all of this into a paper plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:49.26,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,If I just send this flying...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:52.30,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also fly to even greater heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.67,0:08:57.80,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,She's in denial.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:09:00.53,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:02.52,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, light of youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:10.11,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:23.37,Institute,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,0)\blur0.7\frx358\fry356\frz10.263\pos(574,160)}Shinonome Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:25.37,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,Nano.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:27.90,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,What should we play?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:31.38,Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)\pos(568,417)}An Everyday\NCold
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:40.67,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Blow your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:45.43,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, you should have some medicine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:47.27,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,What should we play?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.66,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Please take your medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.66,0:09:51.57,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,Sakamoto, what should we play?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:53.57,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:54.69,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Sakamoto-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:55.95,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:10:00.62,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you've had a runny nose since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:04.69,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to hurry up and go to bed, but you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.69,0:10:07.45,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,You won't eat properly either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:09.25,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:12.61,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go over there and play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:14.13,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:18.58,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get the water now, so make sure you take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:25.36,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,But he said that I don't have that bad of a cold, so I don't need to take medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:26.47,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:27.50,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,Sakamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:28.23,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:29.90,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Sakamoto-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:31.56,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I didn't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:36.94,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,He also said he loves medicine, so he wants to drink my medicine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:38.11,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,When did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:39.78,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Sakamoto-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.11,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,You believe that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:46.80,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,And after that, he said that no matter what you say, he likes medicine so much that he'll{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:54.69,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:59.17,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, please take your medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:02.00,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, you're the one who'll suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:06.77,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,But the medicine's a little bitter and I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:08.27,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:11.62,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be over soon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:13.95,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:15.32,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:16.98,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}are{\i0} lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:20.25,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,Last time, it wasn't over quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.25,0:11:25.02,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,All right, if you take this you'll feel better in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:26.12,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,Is it tasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:30.97,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,I wrapped it in a wafer, so there's no taste at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.97,0:11:33.50,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,You just need to swallow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:34.75,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.37,0:11:37.92,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go. Say "Ah".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:42.71,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,All right, swallow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:54.03,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,No, swallow it with water!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:57.35,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, if you don't hurry, the wafer will melt and{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:05.91,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,Nano, you're a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:08.66,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,That happened because you didn't swallow it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:11.37,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:12.79,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:14.73,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:15.67,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:18.17,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:21.01,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,You like sharks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:23.95,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,Sharks? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:27.54,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know? Sharks hardly ever get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:28.52,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.52,0:12:29.55,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:32.96,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,When they're only hurt a little bit, they heal very quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:35.02,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,However, humans are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:37.98,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,That's because we're not as cool as sharks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:39.39,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:42.62,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,For that reason, humans have to eat many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:45.29,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,When they get sick, they have to{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:46.57,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:54.79,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Sakamoto-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:12:59.14,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll take some as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:01.21,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,So please take your medicine, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:04.68,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if we both do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:11.10,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,Since I can't drink it and Nano can, I think Nano should drink it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:13.24,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,That won't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.24,0:13:16.12,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,Then Sakamoto should take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:17.90,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Why would {\i1}I{\i0} take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:22.40,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep this up, your cold won't get any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.83,0:13:26.45,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't {\i1}care{\i0} if my cold doesn't get any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:32.03,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Sakamoto-san, please get me a tissue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:33.16,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:39.18,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Sakamoto-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:41.09,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I can't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:48.12,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,If you wipe it there, it'll get dirty, won't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:52.43,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,It's not really dirty... and I'm {\i1}not{\i0} taking the medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:55.07,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:58.06,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not going to take your medicine, we'll go without snacks today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.14,0:14:02.32,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,I even made pudding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.81,0:14:04.78,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,Pudding...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:07.60,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,He said it was okay for me to eat snacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:10.02,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Who said that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:13.16,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to blame me again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:15.66,Institute,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.7\frx358\fry356\frz10.263\pos(574,160)}Shinonome Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:17.00,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:19.09,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:21.42,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:23.92,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,She's not even eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:25.42,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:28.76,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,She's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.58,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Girl. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:34.63,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one at fault here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.63,0:14:36.74,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you force her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:38.94,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,...that brat won't take her medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:41.12,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,So it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:43.19,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,But... what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.74,0:14:47.04,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Persuading her now will be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:48.28,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,There is only one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:49.53,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,There's a way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:53.78,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Mix it in with her snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:56.90,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:15:01.67,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Dock it with her favourite food and camouflage it as a ride-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:03.45,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Call it "Operation Snack Mash-up".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:06.69,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, Sakamoto-san! You're an incredible strategist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:09.05,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,You're hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:12.26,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go and make that right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:13.28,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:14.10,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:16.52,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,You'll only have one chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:17.94,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,If you're found out, you won't get another.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:19.18,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:21.19,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:25.38,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,Shark.... Shark...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:26.69,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.04,0:15:27.94,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Here she comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:30.70,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for a snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:32.69,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want some pudding?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:35.62,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:37.05,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:38.62,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:41.21,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,Pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:45.09,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even hidden!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:48.63,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Girl, follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:50.34,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,That was a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:53.17,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:55.59,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Do you {\i1}want{\i0} that brat to see the medicine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.59,0:15:57.01,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do it wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:59.49,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I say you only had one chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:01.77,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone would have doubts about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:05.02,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,You have to mix, mix and sprinkle it inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:07.86,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'll mix it in right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:15.33,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you guys can't do anything without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:18.41,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Really, it's a good thing I'm here{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:18.41,Default-Alt,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Sakamoto-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:30.63,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:31.25,Default-Alt,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,What the{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:32.94,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,This pudding's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:36.15,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,It's crunchy at first, but then it becomes more like pudding. It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.15,0:16:38.21,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:39.58,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:42.48,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Please eat it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:45.98,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,We did it, Sakamoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:48.15,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:51.94,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it sometimes happens like this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:17:13.72,Institute,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.7\frx358\fry356\frz10.263\pos(574,160)}Shinonome Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:58.98,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,Nano, can I have another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:17:00.75,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,Crunchy pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:01.59,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.59,0:17:04.22,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,The next one's not going to be crunchy, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:08.63,Default,Becky Expy,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, Sakamoto-san said that the crunchy pudding was better!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:09.46,Default,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,Me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:11.24,Default,Nano,0000,0000,0000,,Sakamoto-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:13.72,Default-Alt,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Shinonome Institute had another peaceful day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:26.73,Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,250)\pos(533,199)}An Everyday\NReservation
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:32.89,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.89,0:17:35.53,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,The train's due to come soon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:38.07,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, about a minute left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:49.21,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,There's absolutely nobody here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:50.55,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:53.09,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't as many people around in the afternoon, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:55.61,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that we're alone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:58.01,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:02.71,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,...even if I do this, nobody will get mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:05.10,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, Yukko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:08.06,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,You do it too, Mio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:10.34,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's looking anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.34,0:18:11.91,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:12.82,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.66,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.98,0:18:18.62,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,How'd I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.62,0:18:20.45,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Mio-chan, that's not quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:24.35,Default,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:38.96,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-chan, do you like trains?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.96,0:18:40.29,Default,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,A bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:52.31,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,There's nobody here. It's like we've reserved it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:57.78,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,The tension's rising!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:01.50,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Mio-chan, Mio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:03.12,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play, let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:07.45,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:09.12,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:19.48,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-chan, you're the referee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.48,0:19:20.71,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Watch us...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.11,0:19:32.27,Default,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Bunk bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:38.53,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Triple-decker bunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.53,0:19:54.27,Default,Yukko,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I feel as if I'm the only one losing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:04.68,Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1700,0)\pos(484,277)}Nichijou\NEpisode 0
